  "prompt": "If my boyfriend chooses to spend my birthday with someone else is that a bad sign?",
  "response": "Generally, yes, that could be a bad sign. A partner typically prioritizes their significant other's birthday and wants to celebrate with them. His choice to spend your birthday with someone else might indicate:\n\n1. Lack of care or consideration for your feelings\n2. Possible issues with commitment\n3. Not valuing your relationship\n4. Potential communication problems\n\nHowever, context matters. Some questions to consider:\n- Did he explain why he can't be with you?\n- Is there a legitimate reason like work or a family emergency?\n- Have you discussed your feelings about this?\n\nThe best approach is to have an honest conversation with him about how his actions make you feel and understand his perspective.",
